text: Ok I wasnt gonna watch it but now I have to cause I wanna see "cersei" (lena Headey) going badass on everyone. :D As for people who say "too much feminism power"? I think thats just the case of whining and not able to share what you were used to get in over abundance. Representation. Come back to me with your argument of too much feminist power when we get every month a movie with only women in it as characters while the men stay either absent, silent or flat plot devices or sexual objects. (my point here is, 300 is in no way a feministic movie. also for clearance what I gather from some comments: 300 as a whole is really fictional. Its a fantasy movie who is at best very very loosely based on a few historical facts who on top are very biased. For example, The persian empire as the bad guys? Ugh yeah no, not really. they were agressors, but they also outlawed slavery (took the greeks and their brethren of western civilisation only another roughly 2000 years) when they conquered they left their enemies political structure (Kings and governments )largely intact and only wanted them to pay taxes thats why the Persian king was called king of kings. They improved infrastructure and life in general for their people. Seriously if you want to pick a place to live in that time of history? The persian empire is probably the best place to live. But as I see 300 largely as fantasy movie I will still enjoy it. And I say to hell with accuracy, (and yeah me is not complaining to see the spartans in their "spartan" armor.)

text: When the Ionian Dream of freedom comes crumbling down in flames, hunted by the vast Persian Empire, the Ionian metropolis of Athens, their last refuge, faces imminent destruction and oblivion for daring to challenge despotism and inventing democracy and the unheard notion of people choosing freely for their lives and their future. Facing the entire known world, they choose the unthinkable. To stand. To protect their way of life and their invention and not to submit. If Athens fall, Greece and its ideals would never be, Europe and western civilization would end up nothing more than a big dynasty like China. In the time of great need, despite being rival city-states, the Doric Spartans rise to the occation and assume an impossible task. Just the way they like them to be. Lets see now, Spartan epic heroism + Athenian uncanny ingenuity VS the statistically impossible.  Aeschylus; "BECAUSE ONLY WE, CONTRARY TO THE BARBARIANS, NEVER COUNT THE ENEMY IN BATTLE”

text: To get the historical perspectives of the movie, just imagine the following scenario:  Almost the WHOLE WORLD is under Chinese occupation; EUROPE, ASIA, AFRICA, AUSTRALIA are parts of the CHINESE EMPIRE. The only free countries are the ones located in North & south America and CHINESE EMPIRE is about to strike them hard. The only relative obstacle is the US and its states.  The US states are more independent and sometimes are in direct fight against its other, because they have different political & social ethics. 2 states are the dominant ones: NY in the East (ATHENS) & LA in the West (SPARTA). NY is more liberal, democratic & artistic society and LA is more conservative & militarized. NY has the best navy forces & LA has the best army.  The Chinese Empire invades, everyone is afraid and about to give up and then LA (SPARTA) sends few men for a last stand, to awaken the rest of the states with their sacrifice. If they don’t resist, every country in North & South America will collapse and surrender in just a few weeks. The last stand take place in Florida (Thermopylae) and then the Chinese forces march to conquer NY. A united force of NY (Athenians) and LA (Spartans) {NY leads the force} decide to face them in a sea battle. They win but the main Chinese force is still intact and camped somewhere in Mississippi.  The next months, united armies under LA (SPARTA) leadership face them in a battle (Plataea) and although outnumbered 12:1 they defeat them and throw them out of US, destroying practically their dreams for WORLD DOMINATION.  The next 50 years there is a constant war between NY & LA for territorial purposes ( NY has more blame for this war) and finally LA wins. But in fact there is no winner and the Chinese Empire is happy to see both states suffer, thinking that will have a better chance to invade in the future. But from this war, another dominant state is emerging that rules for the next 20 years and this is CHICAGO (THEVA).  CHINESE EMPIRE interferes constantly with US and trying to harm them, but then the dominant state of US becomes for the first time KENTACKY (MACEDONIA), which is consider from the other states , the redneck state and for the last 400 years hasn’t got any great achievements to show.  But KENTACKY (MACEDONIA) succeeds ( FOR THE FIRST TIME IN HISTORY OF US) to unite all of the states and they strike Chinese Empire in order to free the rest of the world.
